Changing your pom to the following:

&lt;!-- language: xml-lang --&gt;

    &lt;plugin&gt;
		&lt;groupId&gt;org.codehaus.mojo&lt;/groupId&gt;
		&lt;artifactId&gt;exec-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
		&lt;version&gt;1.5.0&lt;/version&gt;
		&lt;executions&gt;
			&lt;execution&gt;
				&lt;id&gt;StartHub&lt;/id&gt;
				&lt;phase&gt;test&lt;/phase&gt;
				&lt;goals&gt;
					&lt;goal&gt;exec&lt;/goal&gt;
				&lt;/goals&gt;
				&lt;configuration&gt;
					&lt;executable&gt;java&lt;/executable&gt;
					&lt;arguments&gt;
						&lt;argument&gt;-version&lt;/argument&gt;
					&lt;/arguments&gt;
				&lt;/configuration&gt;
			&lt;/execution&gt;
